questionText:
In the circle with center O shown below, the area of sector AOB is 15π square units. If the radius of the circle is 6 units, what is the measure of angle AOB in degrees?

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Circle
        A -- Radius --> O
        B -- Radius --> O
        O -- Arc --> A
        O -- Arc --> B
    end
    style O fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style A fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style B fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    linkStyle 0 stroke-width:2px,stroke:black;
    linkStyle 1 stroke-width:2px,stroke:black;
    linkStyle 2 stroke-width:2px,stroke:black;
    linkStyle 3 stroke-width:2px,stroke:black;
    classDef sector fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;
    class O,A,B sector;
```
